'''Sebastian Dickins''' was a stuntman who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']], doubling for [[Ian McDiarmid]] during the more acrobatic stunts required for his character ([[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]) during that film.<ref name="Episode III">{{Film|III}}</ref>

